back\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104exa1665702598712.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/exa1665702598712.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/exa1665702598712.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"exa1665702598712\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                     \n $curocc\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"exa1665702598712___curocc_256482\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the sequence number of the current occurrence in the hitlist.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"exa1665702598712__topic_d81410e1_d81411e1_d81412e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exa1665702598712__p_d81413e1_d81414e1_d81415e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curocc</span> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exa1665702598712__p_d81416e1_d81417e1_d81418e1\">Example: message <code class=\"ph codeph\">\"Number %%$curocc of %%$totocc\"</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"exa1665702598712__topic_d53667e1_d53668e1_d53669e1_d53670e1_d53671e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d387584e81\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"exa1665702598712__d6456e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"exa1665702598712__d6456e20__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"exa1665702598712__d6456e20__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"exa1665702598712__d6456e20__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__d6456e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__d6456e20__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__d6456e20__entry__3\">\n Name of the entity. If omitted, the current entity is used.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"exa1665702598712__topic_d53672e1_d53673e1_d53674e1_d53675e1_d53676e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d387584e135\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"exa1665702598712__li_d33818e1_d33819e1_d33820e1\">Sequence number in the hitlist of the current occurrence.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"exa1665702598712__li_d33821e1_d33822e1_d33823e1\">Empty string (\"\"), if an error occurred, in which case <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8195e1_d8196e1_d8197e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curocc</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8195e1_d8196e1_d8197e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8195e1_d8196e1_d8197e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8195e1_d8196e1_d8197e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8195e1_d8196e1_d8197e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1102</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8195e1_d8196e1_d8197e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_ENTITY&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8195e1_d8196e1_d8197e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"exa1665702598712__topic_d53677e1_d53678e1_d53679e1_d53680e1_d53681e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d387584e216\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exa1665702598712__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"exa1665702598712__topic_d53682e1_d53683e1_d53684e1_d53685e1_d53686e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d387584e226\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"exa1665702598712__p_d81434e1_d81435e1_d81436e1\">The following events affect the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curocc</span>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Events that change <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curocc</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__1\">\n Event\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__2\">\n Action\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__3\">\n Comment\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"2\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">discard</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__2\">\n No change.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__3\">If there is an occurrence following the\n                        discarded occurrence. <div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"exa1665702598712__note_w83ab1b7c11b5b3b9b1b5b1_w84ab1b7c11b5b3b9b1b5_w85ab1b7c11b5b3b9b1_w86ab1b7c11b5b3b9_w87ab1b7c11b5b3_w88ab1b7c11b5_w89ab1b7c11_w90ab1b7_w91ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> If <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">discard</span> is\n                           used outside the read trigger, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> may return\n                              <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> (indicating that there are no following\n                           occurrences) even when there are still occurrences to be read. For more\n                           information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lsx1665702598541.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lsx1665702598541.html\" title=\"Remove one or more occurrences from the component and the hitlist.\">discard</a>. </div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__2\">\n Subtracts 1 from <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curocc</span>.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__3\">\n If there is no occurrence following the discarded occurrence.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__2\">\n Sets <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curocc</span> to 1.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__3\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setocc</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__2\">\n Sets <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curocc</span> to specified occurrence.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__3\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__1\">\n ^ADD_OCC\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__2\">\n Adds 1 to <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curocc</span>.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__3\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totocc</span> is increased by 1.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__1\">\n ^INS_OCC\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__2\">\n No change.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__3\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totocc</span> is increased by 1.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"2\">\n ^NEXT_OCC\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__2\">\n Adds 1 to <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curocc</span>.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__3\">\n If there is a next occurrence present in the component.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__2\">\n No change.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__3\">\n If there is no next occurrence.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"2\">\n ^PREV_OCC\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__2\">\n Subtracts 1 from <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curocc</span>.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__3\">\n If there is a previous occurrence present in the component.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__2\">\n No change.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"exa1665702598712__table_d8198e1_d8199e1_d8200e1__entry__3\">\n If there is no previous occurrence.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"exa1665702598712__section_ozl_4ss_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d387584e440\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curocc</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example shows ProcScript in the getFocus trigger of an\n               entity. The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curocc</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$totocc</span> are used to\n               show the user the position of the current occurrence in relation to other occurrences\n               in the component structure:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"exa1665702598712__pre_yyw_4ss_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger getFocus\n message \"Number %%$curocc of %%$totocc\"\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yrm1665702560304.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>creocc</a><p>Creates an empty occurrence of the specified entity.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fpg1665702560533.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>remocc</a><p>Mark an occurrence of the specified entity for deletion at the next store.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fio1665702598862.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$dbocc</a><p>Return the sequence number of the current occurrence within the set of occurrences retrieved from the database.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vhw1665702560221.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>setocc</a><p>Make a specific occurrence the current occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rmp1665702598941.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$totocc</a><p>Return the number of occurrences of an entity in the component.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527372\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527372\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$curocc Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $curocc Return the sequence number of the current occurrence in the hitlist. $curocc { ( Entity ) } Example: message \"Number %%$curocc of %%$totocc\" Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Name of the entity. If omitted, the current entity is used. Return Values Sequence number in the hitlist of the current occurrence. Empty string (\"\"), if an error occurred, in which case $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Table 2. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following $curocc Value Error constant Meaning -1102 <UPROCERR_ENTITY> The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The following events affect the value of $curocc : Table 3. Events that change $curocc Event Action Comment discard No change. If there is an occurrence following the discarded occurrence. Note: If discard is used outside the read trigger, $status may return 0 (indicating that there are no following occurrences) even when there are still occurrences to be read. For more information, see discard . Subtracts 1 from $curocc . If there is no occurrence following the discarded occurrence. retrieve Sets $curocc to 1. setocc Sets $curocc to specified occurrence. ^ADD_OCC Adds 1 to $curocc . $totocc is increased by 1. ^INS_OCC No change. $totocc is increased by 1. ^NEXT_OCC Adds 1 to $curocc . If there is a next occurrence present in the component. No change. If there is no next occurrence. ^PREV_OCC Subtracts 1 from $curocc . If there is a previous occurrence present in the component. No change. If there is no previous occurrence. Example: Using $curocc The following example shows ProcScript in the getFocus trigger of an entity. The $curocc and $totocc are used to show the user the position of the current occurrence in relation to other occurrences in the component structure: trigger getFocus message \"Number %%$curocc of %%$totocc\" end Copy Related Links creocc Creates an empty occurrence of the specified entity. remocc Mark an occurrence of the specified entity for deletion at the next store. $dbocc Return the sequence number of the current occurrence within the set of occurrences retrieved from the database. setocc Make a specific occurrence the current occurrence. $totocc Return the number of occurrences of an entity in the component. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}